name: Arkefi
description: ArkeFi enables fractional ownership of high-value luxury assets such as art and cars, creating opportunities for investors to earn stable returns of 6-10%. Using its innovative Fractional Option Financing (FOF) model, ArkeFi provides asset owners with liquidity while offering tokenized, secure investments. Backed by insured storage and AI-driven analytics, ArkeFi makes exclusive markets more accessible and profitable.
